name: LORE CARD 010: POWERS
description: A data scan of a being referred to as ‘Protocol’, believed to be a magic eradicating AI set on seeking out any manifestations of the ‘magic’ phenomena we have been witnessing and eliminating them with lethal force.  The creator of the AI is unknown, but nobles have expressed frustration that the protocol doesn’t seem to be available to the existing hierarchy of colony society other than The Queen.
